            <p>Your account has been successfully restored</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <div class="greeting">
                Hello {{firstName}},
            </div>

            {{#if organizationName}}
            <div class="organization-branding">
                {{#if organizationLogo}}
                <img src="{{organizationLogo}}" alt="{{organizationName}}" class="organization-logo">
                {{/if}}
                <div class="organization-name">{{organizationName}}</div>
                {{#if organizationWebsite}}
                <div style="font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280;">
                    <a href="{{organizationWebsite}}" style="color: #6366f1; text-decoration: none;">{{organizationWebsite}}</a>
                </div>
                {{/if}}
            </div>
            {{/if}}
            
            <div class="message">
                Great news! ðŸŒŸ Your {{companyName}} account has been successfully restored and is now active again. We're thrilled to welcome you back to our learning community and can't wait to see you continue your educational journey with us.
            </div>
            
            <div class="welcome-back-card">
                <div class="welcome-icon">ðŸš€</div>
                <div class="welcome-title">Account Successfully Restored</div>
                <div class="welcome-message">
                    You now have full access to all your courses, progress, achievements, and learning materials. Everything is exactly as you left it - your hard work and progress have been safely preserved.
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="account-info">
                <h3>Account Details</h3>
                <div class="account-detail">
                    <div class="account-detail-label">Full Name</div>
                    <div class="account-detail-value">{{firstName}} {{lastName}}</div>
                </div>
                <div class="account-detail">
                    <div class="account-detail-label">Email Address</div>
                    <div class="account-detail-value">{{userEmail}}</div>
                </div>
                {{#if organizationName}}
                <div class="account-detail">
                    <div class="account-detail-label">Organization</div>
                    <div class="account-detail-value">{{organizationName}}</div>
                </div>
                {{/if}}
                {{#if branchName}}
                <div class="account-detail">
                    <div class="account-detail-label">Branch</div>
                    <div class="account-detail-value">{{branchName}}</div>
                </div>
                {{/if}}
                {{#if restoredBy}}
                <div class="account-detail">
                    <div class="account-detail-label">Restored By</div>
                    <div class="account-detail-value">{{restoredBy}}</div>
                </div>
                {{/if}}
            </div>

            <div class="benefits">
                <h4>ðŸŽ¯ What's Available to You Now</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li>Access to all your enrolled courses and learning materials</li>
                    <li>Your complete learning progress and achievement history</li>
                    <li>Ability to take tests and assessments</li>
                    <li>Full dashboard functionality and reporting</li>
                    <li>Community features and collaboration tools</li>
                    <li>All your certificates and accomplishments</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="message">
                <strong>Ready to dive back in?</strong> Your learning journey continues right where you left off. Whether you want to complete courses you were working on or explore new learning opportunities, we're here to support your growth and success every step of the way.
            </div>

            <div class="cta-section">
                <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" class="cta-button">Access Dashboard</a>
                <a href="{{profileUrl}}" class="cta-button primary">Update Profile</a>
            </div>

            <div class="quick-links">
                <h3>Quick Access Links</h3>
                <div class="links-grid">
                    <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" class="quick-link-button primary">Dashboard</a>
                    <a href="{{profileUrl}}" class="quick-link-button">Profile</a>
                    {{#if organizationWebsite}}
                    <a href="{{organizationWebsite}}" class="quick-link-button">{{organizationName}}</a>
                    {{/if}}
                    {{#if companyUrl}}
                    <a href="{{companyUrl}}" class="quick-link-button">Visit {{companyName}}</a>
                    {{/if}}
                    <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}" class="quick-link-button success">Contact Support</a>
                    {{#if unsubscribeUrl}}
                    <a href="{{unsubscribeUrl}}" class="quick-link-button warning">Unsubscribe</a>
                    {{/if}}
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="message">
                If you have any questions or need assistance getting back into your learning routine, our support team is always here to help. We're genuinely excited to have you back and look forward to supporting your continued growth and success! ðŸ’ª
            </div>
            
            <div class="message">
                Welcome back to the {{companyName}} community! Let's make this next chapter of your learning journey even more amazing than the last. ðŸŒŸ
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>This notification was sent to {{userEmail}}{{#if restoredBy}} by {{restoredBy}}{{/if}}{{#if organizationName}} from {{organizationName}}{{/if}}</p>
            <p>Need help? Contact us at <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">{{supportEmail}}</a></p>
            <p>{{#if organizationName}}{{organizationName}} - {{/if}}{{companyName}} - Empowering Learning Through Assessment</p>
            {{#if unsubscribeUrl}}<p><a href="{{unsubscribeUrl}}">Unsubscribe</a> from these notifications</p>{{/if}}
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 